## Development

### Web Application Development
The web version is built with Flask and can be modified by editing files in `final_distribution/web_version/`.

### Desktop Application Development
The desktop version is built with Tkinter and can be modified by editing files in `medical_lab_system/`.

## Building Desktop Applications

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.7+
- PyInstaller (`pip install pyinstaller`)

### Windows
```bash
python build_executables/build_windows.py
```

### macOS
```bash
python build_executables/build_macos.py
```

## Docker Deployment

### Build and Run
```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

### Run in Background
```bash
docker-compose up -d --build
```

### Stop Services
```bash
docker-compose down
```

